    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained by its previous owner. The exterior presents well, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches from normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear or odors, and all electronics are fully functional. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
